flowchart TD
  A[Inputs: risk tier + confidence band] --> B{Risk Tier}
  
  B -- Low --> L[Action: none<br/>Reversible]
  
  B -- Medium --> M{Confidence}
  M -- High/Med --> MF[Action: friction<br/>Reversible]
  M -- Low --> MR[Action: human review<br/>Abstain under uncertainty]
  
  B -- High --> H{Confidence}
  H -- High --> HL[Action: limit<br/>Reversible in prototype<br/>Policy sign-off flag]
  H -- Med/Low --> HR[Action: human review<br/>HITL required]
  
  MR --> X[Moderator decision + audit]
  HR --> X
  HL --> X
  MF --> X
  L --> X

  X --> Y[Outcome monitoring<br/>reports, violations, appeals]
